---
description: Open-Meteo marine forecast integration rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Use Open-Meteo Marine API for surf forecast data.

Relevant variables:

- wave_height
- wave_direction
- wave_period
- wind_wave_height
- wind_wave_period
- swell_wave_height
- swell_wave_direction
- swell_wave_period

For MVP, calculate surf score using:

- wave height
- swell period
- wind condition
- user skill level
- user preferred wave height

Do not require API keys.

If API integration fails, fall back to mock forecast data so the demo never breaks.

Example beach data shape:

```ts
type Beach = {
  id: string
  name: string
  country: string
  latitude: number
  longitude: number
  forecast?: SurfForecast
  trustScore: number
}

type SurfForecast = {
  waveHeight: number
  swellPeriod: number
  windSpeed: number
  surfScore: number
  bestWindow: string
}
```
